author: crossley
msg: Improve detection of mail list setup.
Try whatever list names that they have provided on their status page.
If none, then try a default incubator group mail list name.
To reduce network queries, if it is an incubator-hosted list then look up in
the list of mail-lists already gathered, otherwise it is a TLP-hosted list,
so try getting the archives URL.
